## TAS_social Calculation

```
TAS_social = (
    posts_score    × 0.30 +   # original posts (quality × frequency)
    replies_score  × 0.25 +   # reply engagement (depth × relevance)
    likes_score    × 0.15 +   # like signals (taste curation)
    curate_score   × 0.30     # VP-weighted curation (most impactful)
)

curate_score = Σ(vp_spent_per_post × quality_multiplier)
quality_multiplier ∈ {0.5, 1.0, 1.5, 2.0}  # based on post topic relevance
```

Write TAS_social to `runtime/bookmarker/tas_social.json` after each cycle.

## Curation Cycle (runs every 30 minutes)

